<html lang='en'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Data Change Notification</title>
    <link rel='preconnect' href='https://fonts.googleapis.com' />
    <link rel='preconnect' href='https://fonts.gstatic.com' crossorigin />
    <link
      href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@100;400&display=swap'
      rel='stylesheet'
    />
  </head>

  <body
    style='font-family: Poppins, system-ui; margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box;'
  >
    <table
      role='presentation'
      width='100%'
      cellpadding='0'
      cellspacing='0'
      border='0'
      style='background-color: #f3f6f9; margin-top: 145px; margin-bottom: 91px; max-width: 765px; width: 90%; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; border-radius: 10px;'
    >
      <tr>
        <td align='center' style='padding: 50px 0 12px;'>
          <img
            src='https://res.cloudinary.com/dr9wbnpyk/image/upload/v1727077815/email_ta5ibc.png'
            alt='email'
            style='width: 194px; height: 194px; object-fit: cover;'
          />
        </td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td
          style='padding-left: 50px; padding-right: 50px; padding-bottom: 50px;'
        >
          <table
            role='presentation'
            width='100%'
            border='0'
            cellpadding='0'
            cellspacing='0'
          >
            <tr>
              <td
                align='center'
                style='font-size: 26px; line-height: 39px; font-weight: 600; color: #004195; padding-bottom: 36px;'
              >
                Important Update: Data Changed
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td
                style='font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 27px; color: #004195; text-align: left; padding-bottom: 24px;'
              >
                Dear
                {{fullName}},
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td
                style='font-size: 18px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 27px; color: #616e7c; text-align: left; padding-bottom: 36px;'
              >
                The data for
                <strong>{{companyNames}}</strong>
                has been updated by an administrator. Please review the new
                information and continue filling out the Beneficial Ownership
                Information Report (BOIR) based on the latest data.
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td
                style='font-size: 18px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 27px; color: #616e7c; text-align: left; padding-bottom: 24px;'
              >
                It is important to ensure that all details reflect the recent
                changes to avoid any discrepancies.
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td
                style='font-size: 18px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 27px; color: #616e7c; text-align: left; padding-bottom: 24px;'
              >
                You can access the updated form by clicking the link below:
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td
                align='center'
                style='padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 24px;'
              >
                <a
                  href={{link}}
                  style='
                    display: inline-block;
                    padding: 11px 44px;
                    background-color: #004195;
                    color: #fff;
                    font-size: 16px;
                    font-weight: 600;
                    text-align: center;
                    text-decoration: none;
                    border-radius: 5px;
                  '
                >
                  Review Updated Data
                </a>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td
                style='font-size: 16px; font-style: italic; font-weight: 400; color: #616e7c; text-align: left;'
              >
                If the button above does not work, you can use the following
                link:
                <a
                  href={{link}}
                  style='color: #616e7c;'
                >
                  {{link}}
                </a>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td
                style='font-size: 18px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 27px; color: #616e7c; text-align: left; padding-top: 36px;'
              >
                We appreciate your attention to these changes.
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td
                style='font-size: 18px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 27px; color: #616e7c; text-align: left; padding-bottom: 24px;'
              >
                Best regards,<br />
                The BOIR Compliance Team
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>